Class PersonDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.erp.light.view.dto.PersonDTO

  • public class PersonDTO
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a DTO representation of the entity Person.
    It is mainly used to transmit data between the frontend and backend.

    Matthias Schnöll
